data.description: This beautiful property is ready for your personal touches and could be perfect to flip or be a rental. This 4 bed 2 bath home is in need of REPAIRS but has so much potential. Home has a new HVAC and has had roof repairs completed already. Close to dining, shopping, interstate access and Southeastern University is right around the corner. Large 30x60 insulated shop is also part of this almost acre property. Front porch wraps around the entire front of the home, and the property has beautiful mature trees and a metal roof. Come put your personal touches on this home and schedule a tour today! The home is missing some flooring and additional room that was added needs to be painted and the primary bedroom as well from the previous repairs made.
